        <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para>The constructor initializes the memory slab by calling RTOS function k_msgq_init. This function initializes the memory slab object, prior to its first use. It returns the memory slab administration structure my_slab. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
